cs.DB, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.CR 

This paper is about entity resolution, which is a problem in database systems. Therefore, cs.DB is the most likely sub-category. The paper also proposes a machine learning-based approach, which suggests that it could belong to cs.AI or cs.LG. The paper also discusses the evaluation of the proposed approach on real data, which suggests that it could belong to cs.IR. Finally, the paper discusses the risk analysis problem, which could also suggest that it belongs to cs.CR.
